        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "彼得對她說：「你告訴我，你們賣田地的價銀就是這些嗎？」她說：「就是這些。」"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "And Peter responded to her, “Tell me whether you sold the land for such and such a price?” And she said, “Yes, that was the price.”"
      },
