        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Peter asked her, “Tell me, is this the price you and Ananias got for the land?” “Yes,” she said, “that is the price.”"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Peter asked her, “Was this the price you and your husband received for your land?” “Yes,” she replied, “that was the price.”"
